sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant Middleware as Idempotency Middleware
    participant Storage as Storage (Redis/Postgres)
    participant API as Business Logic (API)

    Note over Client, API: Request Phase
    Client->>Middleware: HTTP Request + X-Idempotency-Key
    Middleware->>Storage: GetRecordAsync(key)
    Storage-->>Middleware: Return Record (Data or Null)

    alt Key Already Exists
        Note right of Middleware: Cache Hit
        Middleware-->>Client: 200 OK (Cached Response Body)
    else Key is New
        Note right of Middleware: Cache Miss
        Middleware->>API: Forward to Next()
        API-->>Middleware: Response (Result)
        Middleware->>Storage: SaveRecordAsync(key, response)
        Middleware-->>Client: Original Response
    end